Lexian's build of dwm
Nothing special about this build of dwm.
---------------------------------------
Patches and features
- fullgaps/ This patch adds gaps between client windows.
- nomonocleborders/ Removes window border when using Monocle (https://gist.github.com/SebastianJarsve/497b2014774c849df0132d7118cbab65#file-dwm-nomonocleborders-20190607-cb3f58a-diff)
---------------------------------------
Installation
- git clone https://github.com/lLexian/dwm.git
- cd dwm
- sudo make install
